      "role": "user",
      "content": "friend or family? they don't get it. they keep telling me \"it gets better\" or \"give it time\" but time is the problem. every minute that passes just makes the silence louder. it feels so pointless. like i'm just waiting for a life to start that already ended when he died. i feel like i'm just taking up space.",
